[package]
name = "hypridle"
version = "0.1.0"
description = "hypridle — idle daemon; locks via hyprlock after 5 min"

[[link]]
source = ".config/hypr/hypridle.conf"
target = ".config/hypr/hypridle.conf"

---

# hypridle

One file. `lock_cmd = pidof hyprlock || hyprlock` — depends on
the `hyprlock` package being linked + the binary on PATH.
Started via `exec-once = ... & hypridle` in hyprland.conf.

Shares `~/.config/hypr/`.
